data.description: Exciting opportunity! This gem with 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and 2536 sq ft in desirable Morgan Hill awaits your personal touch. Situated on a large fenced in lot, this home features 2 alrge living rooms, a large bonus room, a storm shelter, a brand new roof, a brand new HVAC, and more! Ready for some TLC and updates, this home offers the chance to add equity and transform it into your dream haven. Don't miss out on this canvas for creativity!
